1. *Drveće* u parku je predivno. (*Trees* in the park are beautiful.)
2. U mom dvorištu raste puno *drveća*. (There are many *trees* growing in my yard.)
3. Vidjela sam prekrasno *drveće* dok sam bila u šetnji. (I saw beautiful *trees* while I was out for a walk.)
4. Ukoliko se bavite sečom *drveća*, morate biti oprezni. (If you're involved in cutting down *trees*, you need to be careful.)
5. Jesi li primijetio da je *drveće* počelo mijenjati boje? (Have you noticed that the *trees* have started to change color?)
6. Kada sam bila mala, volela sam da se penjem po *drveću*. (When I was little, I loved climbing *trees*.)
7. *Drveće* u šumi pruža utočište mnogim životinjama. (*Trees* in the forest provide a shelter for many animals.)
8. Treba mi nekoliko metara *drveća* za gradnju kuće. (I need a few meters of *wood* for building a house.)